# A Project Tracking Application

## Introduction
This is an active (a.k.a still learning) web application. This web application will give 
you capability to track any task within any projects, getting reports about unfinished 
task, and another thing related to bug-reporting stuff. Inspired by Atlassian's JIRA.

This application built on this techology stack:
1. Django 1.3.1
2. Postgresql 9.1
At the moment, this application server __very__ basic functionality. No business logic at all.

Future Improvement:
1. Integrate with Twitter's Bootstrap in templates
2. Using openID API
3. Developing a twitter bot for reminder
4. Integrate the file storage with Dropbox.
